$OpenBSD: patch-rust_libnewsboat_src_utils_rs,v 1.2 2021/06/19 11:38:22 tb Exp $

iconv symbols are not part of libc on OpenBSD, so link agaist converters/libiconv
https://github.com/newsboat/newsboat/pull/1678

Index: rust/libnewsboat/src/utils.rs
--- rust/libnewsboat/src/utils.rs.orig
+++ rust/libnewsboat/src/utils.rs
